          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/littlecin/" class=" " title="ccinn">ccinn</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="22312032">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">“谁都喜欢负面新闻，嘴说够受的，实际却很开心”
p93:一种作为实质性家长的责任感，一种对愚昧的暴力和罪行的无法诉诸语言的愤怒。</span>
