              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/19924110/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/haruhituili/" class=" " title="散井">散井</a>
                (是个废宅现充)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="19924110">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">总的来说算是心平气和的，或许莫如说约略近乎‘牢骚’
或许莫如说约略近乎……这是中文吗</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-07-26 10:49</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>总的来说算是心平气和的，或许莫如说约略近乎‘牢骚’</q></blockquote>
或许莫如说约略近乎……这是中文吗
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
